{"tid":2413895,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：港台內部及公開招聘並無一人合乎政治標準 只好由政務官調任","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T04:58:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99aa46d9b3b4d05cc0d9c2c128de65df20e70cd9","tid":2413895,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"當局收逾40份廣播處長職位申請　接見7人無一合適<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長梁卓文表示，政府與廣播處長梁家榮的合約於8月完結，雙方經討論後同意提前幾個月完結。他表示，薪金都是按合約條款安排，政府希望致力於港台內部培養接任人員及晉升，而內部無合適人選之下，當局就進行公開招聘，透過獵頭公司收到41份申請，甄選委員會見過7人，但並無合適人選。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓文表示，在考慮政府內部人選方面，新任處長李百全是資深政務官，行政經驗豐富，形容是合適人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576393-20210219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576393-20210219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69FwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=c9a59c4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576393-20210219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=47a0dbf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576393-20210219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0c0b5c4513bbc962484014ae94cbc80a2939a77f","tid":2413895,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"梗係冇人做啦，又要家境清白，又要唯命是從，又要厚顏無恥"},{"pid":"e2011b2fc443418a08ee3e71ddfe6fac822f700d","tid":2413895,"uid":185652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"居然冇藍永份<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}